	   <tr><td colspan=2>You do a very long and complicated quest (probably the longest and most complicated quest in the entire game) in order to get a spell which summons a weapon which has a charged effect which summons the epic pet.<br><br>The earliest level you could possibly complete the quest is level 46, as you would have to be that level to get into some of the required zones. In all practicality, you would need to be level 55 to complete the quest, since before that level you won't even be able to cast a spell on some of the mobs you will have to kill. I suppose if you have a lot of friends who don't mind you hanging around pretty much doing nothing while they kill the big mobs, you can complete the quest earlier.<br><br>Only a handful of mages on any server have completed the quest. I wouldn't worry too much about it unless you are quite high level (although you can do some research and start picking up bits and pieces of the quest items as early as level 30 or so).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
