	   <tr><td colspan=2>Pets will not disappear every time you cast gate; they will disappear if you happen to gate while bound in a separate zone.<br><br>If you are bound in the same zone you are fighting in, and you gate, your pet will either find his way back to you, or sit where he is until you come within his range again. In the 30s, you will get a spell which will cause your pet to gate to your side (Summon Companion).<br><br>Pets will self-destruct if you zone or if any form of invisibility is cast on you (Invisibility, Camoflauge, Invis to Undead, Invis to Animals).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
