	   <tr><td colspan=2>The only one of these items you should worry about right now is the malachite, as you need it to conjure up your pets. There is a gem vendor on the top floor of the magician's guild in Erudin who sells malachite. Also, there is a small merchant hut in Toxxulia Forest which sells malachite. You can use your Sense Summoned spell to locate Jalen Goldsinger, an enchater NPC who stands outside this hut.<br><br>The other four items you listed (broom, shovel, torch, stein) are called Focus Items and are the result of four quests given in the Temple of Solusek Ro, located inside Lavastorm Mountains. You shouldn't even worry about them until you are in your late 20s or early 30s, as they won't even work for you until level 34.<br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
