	   <tr><td colspan=2>Before you give up in frustration from either playing a mage or reading the various posts from people who levelled to 60 in 15 minutes, just sit back and read some good strategies on various sites. Zuranthium has a good guide on this page. www.magecompendium.com has good stuff, EQ Casters Realm and Everlore all have posted mage strategy. One thing to keep in mind is all MoB's are different and pose unique problems. Everlore's bestiary is a great place for MoB research (by zone) so you can get an idea of what to expect and how to work each opponent. Mages are a challenge, but lots of fun. I've done half my career solo and half grouped and it all works out about the same. Keep trying. Just my 2cp.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Aaneldarie Tura'Seorsa<br>29th Season Magician&nbsp;&nbsp;Vazaelle</td></tr>
