	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings young mage!<br>Actually, with that much platinum, you can buy stuff that will last you until well into your 40s. One thing you should look for are +int rings/earring. You can get a couple of earrings that are +4 int/+2 str, which would be great because you will need a little boost in your str for carrying loot. They are called golden sapphire earrings I believe. Not sure on the cost on your server, but I have gotten them for about 150pp an earring. You can also get you a runed circlet that is +4 int/wis that is good, should cost you about 100pp at most. Or, if you are lucky, you can purchase you your mage robe for about 350pp to 500pp. Again the prices may vary on your server. I play on Bertox so the economy is a lot different. lol But the main thing I would use your money on is to get +int rings, earring, necklace, or bracers. If you can get good deals, then you may be able to buy stuff that will last you WELL past your 20s.<br><br>Hope it helps.<br><br>Vaelek<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
